Package: viu
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Command-line image viewer written in Rust
 viu is a small command-line application that displays images directly in the
 terminal. It supports various protocols including Kitty, iTerm2, and Sixel,
 with a fallback to Unicode block characters for unsupported terminals.
